snippet.title: Odysseus Kosmos and his Robot Quest - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/645820
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.herocraft.game.free.odysseus1

Sci-fi comedy quest in a classic adventure game. A nearby dark hole threatens with sending your ship adrift to deep space and only you, lazy ship engineer Odysseus Kosmos, and your service robot Barton Quest, can stop it!
